<codeline><highlight class="normal">Any<sp/>license<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>&quot;viral&quot;<sp/>to<sp/>modifications</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">causes<sp/>worries<sp/>for<sp/>lawyers,<sp/>even<sp/>if<sp/>their<sp/>programmers</highlight></codeline>
