<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>license:<sp/>you<sp/>are<sp/>granted<sp/>a<sp/>perpetual,<sp/>irrevocable<sp/>license<sp/>to<sp/>copy,<sp/>modify,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>publish,<sp/>and<sp/>distribute<sp/>this<sp/>file<sp/>as<sp/>you<sp/>see<sp/>fit.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">I<sp/>typically<sp/>place<sp/>this<sp/>declaration<sp/>at<sp/>the<sp/>end<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>initial</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">comment<sp/>block<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>file<sp/>and<sp/>just<sp/>say<sp/>&apos;public<sp/>domain&apos;</highlight></codeline>
