<codeline><highlight class="normal">libraries<sp/>because<sp/>it<sp/>was<sp/>only<sp/>&quot;public<sp/>domain&quot;<sp/>and<sp/>didn&apos;t</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">have<sp/>the<sp/>additional<sp/>fallback<sp/>clause,<sp/>who<sp/>asked<sp/>if</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">I<sp/>could<sp/>dual-license<sp/>it<sp/>under<sp/>a<sp/>traditional<sp/>license.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
